# places_reviews: {1: [u'They are really rule this will be the last time that I will enter this popeyes. The manger was there and told me he was on break so he could not talk the worst ever.', u"Service is mean and cold, bad attitude which I can't stand"], 2: [u'Always filthy in here. Seating sucks. Recommend taking food to go.'], 3: [], 4: [], 5: [u"What can be said about Popeyes that hasn't been said already?  I could write epics about this place...just go and see for yourself.  The chicken is juicy and delicious, the sides are phenomenal, the biscuits are better than most biscuits at higher end establishments.  Sure, it's not healthy, but who cares?  It's amazing.", u'Asian run with an urban clientele but worth the trip for their classic Louisiana fried chicken and sides. ']}
