# places_reviews: {1: [], 2: [], 3: [], 4: [u"Beat BBQ in town. 22 years perfecting their recipe. Pork ribs a must try. Lean and the sauce spicy tangy right. Potato salad has to have some secret ingredient in it. I could have eaten a bowl of it like ice cream. Clean picnic tables. Friendly service. If you like real traditional BBQ this is you're spot.", u'I had the wings, steak, and brisket.  All were amazing.   I wish there was more sauce options though.  '], 5: [u'Best bbq in the USA.  Go there, eat there n try the meat first before you go for the sauce. Great food n service.', u"Love the maxi-burger!!  Love Memphis bbq. Staff is great. It's a neighborhood gem.", u'Arrived at a slow hour, food appeared nearly instantly, and the brisket was so tender & delicious, I could hardly stand it.']}
