# places_reviews: {1: [], 2: [], 3: [u'Be sure to check what your being charged. They added a dollar more on every item I purchased.'], 4: [], 5: [u'Love eating at this place.  Total hole in the wall but the food is amazing and the atmosphere is simple.', u'The best soup around, I get great service by the short guy, but the taller thin one is not so courteous.  The short gentleman is nice all the time.', u'"Jalapeno Chicken Fried Rice" was amazing. If you like it a little spicy this is this perfect dish. Not to spicy but the right zest on the taste buds...Good stuff.', u"I love Wild Pepper (Chinese Food) because the way I feel after I ate here. You can eat a large portion but not feel like you just ate a balloon. You can see and taste the quality of the food. It's a small place but you can seat down and enjoy every single bite of food here. A small groups (about 6) will be much better eating inside. They do take out and I have never been disappointed. Love this chinese food spot. Enjoy it with family and friends...\U0001f60b"]}
